sentence.text: Three loci with high mutation frequencies, the 138665410 negative regulation of transcription, DNA-templated gene variant, the 23862952 MYH6 gene variant, and the 71098693 HYDIN gene variant were found to be significantly associated with sporadic ASD (P<0.05); variants in FOXL2 and MYH6 were found in patients with isolated, sporadic ASD (P<5Ã—10^-4).
